EBANTWINI abathathu kwabane abahaqekayo kuvele izolo ukuthi basuke bengabaseWestern Cape. Lokhu kuvele ezibalweni ezidalulwe nguNgqongqoshe wezeMpilo kuleli, uDkt Zweli Mkhize. Okwamanje isibalo sabashonile sesifinyelele kwaba ngu-17 bese abayisishiyagalolunye ngabaseWestern Cape- okunye ukuthi isibalo esiphezulu sabashonile siqhamuke kulesi sifundazwe. Lokho kuchaza ukuthi u75% wabantu abangu-663 abasanda kutheleleka ngaleli gciwane baqhamuka kulesi sifundazwe esesinenqwaba yabantu asebedlule emhlabeni ngenxa yalolu bhubhane. UMkhize uthe izikhulu ezizobe ziqhamuka emnyangweni wezempilo kuzwelonke zizovakashela kulesi sifundazwe nase-Eastern CapeÂ  ngale mpelasonto. Ngesonto elizayo uMengameli wezwe, uMnuz Cyril Ramaphosa noMkhize bazovakashela kulezi zifundazwe njengoba sikhuphuka ngokushesha isibalo sabantu abahaqwe yiCOVID-19. EWestern Cape sebebalelwa ku-4 497 asebehaqekile futhi lesi sifundazwe sizihola phambili ngokuba nabantu abangu-88 abangasekho emhlabeni, okuyisibalo esiyingxenye yasebeshonile ezweni lonke jikelele. Ngokwezinombolo, iWestern Cape inabantu abangu-503 kwabasanda kutholakala ukuthi sebethelelekile, abangu-663 nabangu-9 kwabangu-17 okusanda kubikwa ukuthi abasekho emhlabeni. Abanye ababili abashonile ngabaseKZN, kuthi abathathu baqhamuke e-Eastern Cape naseGauteng, isifundazwe ngasinye. EGauteng bangu-131 abasanda kutholakala ukuthi sebethelelekile, e-Eastern Cape bangu-60 kuthi eKZN babe ngu-49.  IZIBALO ZAKAMUVA ZIMI KANJE: ABASANDA KUSHONA ABASANDA KUHAQEKA ESABAHAQEKILE ESABASHONILE South Africa 17 663 8895 178 Western Cape 9 503 4497 88 Gauteng 3 131 1851 18 KZN 2 49 1253 42 Eastern Cape 3 60 989 18 Free State 0 0 133 6 Mpumalanga 0 1 60 0 Limpopo 0 2 43 3 N West 0 2 42 0 N Cape 0 0 27 0 INingizimu Afrika seyihlole abantu ababalelwa ku-307 000 , okubandakanya nabangaphezu kuka-15 500 abahlolwe emahoreni abalelwa ku-24. Eqhuba uMkhize uthe babalelwa ku-8.2 million abantu osekukhulunywe nabo ngenhloso yokubheka ukuthi akumele yini bahlolwe. UMkhize uthe zibalelwa ku435 iziguli eziphethwe yiCOVID-19 ezibhedlela.   Ezingu45 zise-high care Ezingu77 zisemaginjini abantu abaxineke kakhulu Ezingu40 zikuma-ventilators 